1.4 Basic Usage
===============

  1. Start greader mode with ‘M-x greader-mode’.
  2. Press ‘C-r <spc>’ to start reading.  If desired, you can change the
     prefix.  See the command ‘greader-set-map-prefix’.
  3. Press ‘<spc>’ to stop reading.


