1.7.8 ‘greader-translate-mode’
------------------------------

‘greader-translate-mode’ is a minor mode that allows for on-the-fly
translation of the buffer being read.  When this mode is active, each
sentence is translated before being sent to the text-to-speech engine.

* Menu:

* Usage: Usage 2.
* Configuration::
