1.8.1 eSpeak / eSpeak NG
------------------------

The default backend on most systems.  Install from your distribution or
from espeak-ng (https://github.com/espeak-ng/espeak-ng).  No additional
Emacs configuration is required beyond having ‘espeak-ng’ on your
‘PATH’.


